| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3567 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5b5af06d-ff60-5a2f-a00d-3e8190484bc2"
